verbose_text: Briefly, pseudoviruses were produced by transfection of the VP1, VP2, VP3 and pSV40-Cluc plasmids into HEK293FT cells using the FuGENE (R) 6 Transfection Reagent (PromegaMadison, WI USA cat # E2692) in a 3:1:1:2 ratio.
